data.description: Welcome home to this charming house on a convenient corner lot in the highly sought after neighborhood of Falcon Landing! Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, it's an ideal haven for families or those seeking a convenient space. The heart of the home is the open concept kitchen, dining, and living room, where culinary adventures await with GAS cooking and an expansive island that's perfect for both meal prep and friendly gatherings.  The oversized master bedroom is a standout feature, offering an abundance of space for both rest and relaxation, with a perfect nook for a sitting area, a full en suite bathroom & large walk-in master closet.   Off the living room, take note of the covered patio in the large backyard where you can sit and sip your morning coffee. :)  This property is conveniently located in the neighborhood just a block from the amenity center (pool/playground area), and has a great location within just a short drive to Alamo Ranch shopping and dining, Lackland, Sea World, Six Flags, and La Cantera.   YOU NEED TO SEE THIS ONE! Schedule your showing asap!
